data.description: Discover refined living in the heart of Mt. Vernon Square with this stunning 2-bedroom corner condo at The Sonata,  thoughtfully designed to maximize both comfort and style, featuring a brand new water heater and expansive floor-to-ceiling windows that not only bring in an abundance of natural light but also offer high ceilings that enhance the open, airy feel of the home. This home is one of the larger floor plans in the building, known for its spacious layout. Situated perfectly on the corner, residents of Apt 505 enjoy pristine views of the developing "forever green" park, which will soon be an accessible community space. The strategic corner placement also provides a vantage point to easily see the street and alley, perfect for greeting visitors or receiving deliveries. Built-in blinds and electric blackout blinds in the primary bedroom ensure both privacy and comfort throughout the seasons. Storage is plentiful, with the kitchen boasting extensive cabinetry and the primary bathroom offering ample under-sink space. Each bedroom features efficient shelving systems that maximize vertical storage space, adding to the overall functionality of the unit. Residents of The Sonata enjoy access to a rooftop terrace with stunning city views, perfect for watching the July 4th fireworks, and benefit from a recently enhanced ADT security system, including a lifetime Aiphone license for the callbox at the front door, a cost already covered and transferable to the new owner. The community is vibrant and supportive, facilitated by an active condo board and the Sonata Google Group, which keeps everyone connected and informed.   The building also features a state-of-the-art fitness center and luxurious communal spaces like a newly updated lobby and an award-winning roof deck, making it not just a place to live, but a place to thrive. Located conveniently among four Metro stations and close to I-395, the Sonata is also just steps away from diverse shopping, dining, and nightlife options. This condo is pet-friendly, accommodating up to two pets with a combined mature weight limit of 75 pounds. It comes with a dedicated parking space. For those with electric vehicles, charging stations can be installed as some owners have already opted for this upgrade.   Welcome to your new home at The Sonata, where comfort meets convenience in a vibrant community setting, complete with all the amenities needed for modern urban living.
